{"tid":254138,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警再拘21名UBER司機　涉嫌非法載客及沒第三者保險駕駛","createTime":"2017-05-23T03:08:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T17:23:37.000Z","uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e731319db478b6b2543645cc7e0194aca9d2dc88","tid":254138,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T03:08:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/201705/11894211_10153510764824330_8906628828498513921_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F201705%2F11894211_10153510764824330_8906628828498513921_o.jpg&h=c0e3fed7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據無綫新聞報道，警方今日再拘捕21名UBER司機，指他們涉嫌觸犯非法載客取酬，以及在沒有第三者保險而駕駛罪。  警方曾於2015年8月，以放蛇方式拘捕7名Uber司機，被控以「駕駛汽車以取酬載客」和「沒有第三者保險而駕駛」兩項罪名，當中5名司機不認罪，但最終被裁罪成，各人被判罰款1萬元及停牌12個月。"},{"pid":"7a0eee1dc781df2d11e3d57147c714257bc05329","tid":254138,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T03:10:50.000Z","msg":"認罪罰幾多"},{"pid":"727fd611122162873861f4d8aef4a63df1f41e29","tid":254138,"uid":34551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T03:23:01.000Z","msg":"拉到車死流浪漢個的士狗未呀警畜<br />\nuber又走去搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3240257a397c74c64d12145d2043ac85ff8a2040","tid":254138,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T03:24:23.000Z","msg":"唔係AIG出左UBER第三者保險保單咩？"},{"pid":"e798fd402b6de063b043d84b86111d9aa1f21d32","tid":254138,"uid":45760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T03:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定係689搞事"},{"pid":"7a9ab0e24488189321a3762f259764c1a4c24985","tid":254138,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T03:27:56.000Z","msg":"仆你個街，今晚仲諗住叫車"},{"pid":"0dca4624fd94d443eb1fc14e28eb660e13a6f191","tid":254138,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"